{"id": 59369, "date": "2025-08-17T04:00:33", "date_gmt": "2025-08-17T11:00:33", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59369"}, "modified": "2026-05-13T17:03:30", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-14T00:03:30", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-17-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/17/kingdom-of-days-august-17-2/", "title": {"rendered": "August 17"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><b>1969:\u00a0</b>Child reluctantly plays a gig at The Student Prince in Asbury Park. Why reluctantly? Because Woodstock was happening at the same time, and that&#8217;s where the band wants to be&#8211;but they honor their commitment.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band wrap up their legendary five-night stand at The Bottom Line in New York City with two final shows. The buzz from these shows will turbocharge Bruce&#8217;s career and the remainder of the Born to Run Tour.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4Y-7c4n2eaE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RD4Y-7c4n2eaE\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the boys play their second night at Red Rocks Amphitheater on the River Tour, but on this night the weather cooperates.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLsxNBNx2akeU6hH1IQ-_RzSrXz3-Te7tL\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>The Born in the U.S.A. Tour&#8217;s ten-night stand at the Brendan Byrne Arena in East Rutherford reaches Night Eight, a show notable for the first-ever performance of &#8220;I&#8217;m Goin&#8217; Down&#8221; and the tour premiere of &#8220;Follow That Dream.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_PJFou1o1JE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and his new touring band bring World Tour 1992 to the Detroit area for their first of two shows at The Palace of Auburn Hills. Watch the soundcheck, pre-show interview, and concert footage below.</p>\n<div id=\"v-XxssRVjw-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/XxssRVjw?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cVLXiCqsTpY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20454\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1992-08-17a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1992-08-17a.png?fit=1382%2C1403&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1382,1403\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1992-08-17a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1992-08-17a.png?fit=758%2C769&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20454 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1992-08-17a.png?resize=758%2C770&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"770\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1992-08-17a.png?w=1382&amp;ssl=1 1382w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1992-08-17a.png?resize=296%2C300&amp;ssl=1 296w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-con