, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Bruce postpones a scheduled Reunion show in Detroit to the following month due to &#8220;scheduling conflicts.&#8221;</p>\n<p><strong>2003:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of only two Rising Tour stadium shows on the west coast, this one at Dodger Stadium in Los Angeles.</p>\n<div id=\"v-ijPr8cpo-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/ijPr8cpo?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20456\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2003-08-17a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17a.png?fit=759%2C1117&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"759,1117\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2003-08-17a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17a.png?fit=696%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20456 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17a.png?resize=758%2C1116&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1116\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17a.png?w=759&amp;ssl=1 759w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17a.png?resize=204%2C300&amp;ssl=1 204w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17a.png?resize=696%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 696w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20457\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2003-08-17b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17b.png?fit=1235%2C1645&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1235,1645\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2003-08-17b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17b.png?fit=758%2C1009&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20457 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17b.png?resize=758%2C1010&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1010\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17b.png?w=1235&amp;ssl=1 1235w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17b.png?resize=225%2C300&amp;ssl=1 225w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17b.png?resize=769%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 769w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17b.png?resize=768%2C1023&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17b.png?resize=1153%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1153w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-08-17b.png?resize=900%2C1200&amp;ssl=1 900w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>2021:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>resumes its limited return engagement at the St. James Theater in New York City after a month-long break. During the hiatus, the pandemic has resurged and masks are a requirement among the audience again. Bruce also winks at the recent &#8220;Thunder Road&#8221; debate, definitively and repetitively singing &#8220;sways&#8221; to put the matter to rest.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-59369-3\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/05-Thunder-Road.mp3?_=3\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/05-Thunder-Road.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/05-Thunder-Road.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"54089\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/daily_record_2021_08_27_x7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Daily_Record_2021_08_27_X7-scaled.jpg?fit=1264%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1264,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Daily_Record_2021_08_27_X7\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Daily_Record_2021_08_27_X7-scaled.jpg?fit=505%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-54089\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Daily_Record_2021_08_27_X7-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C1535&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1535\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Daily_Record_2021_08_27_X7-scaled.jpg?w=1264&amp;ssl=1 1264w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Daily_Record_2021_08_27_X7-scaled.jpg?resize=148%2C300&amp;ssl=1 148w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Daily_Record_2021_08_27_X7-scaled.jpg?resize=505%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 505w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Daily_Record_2021_08_27_X7-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1556&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Daily_Record_2021_08_27_X7-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 758w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Bruce plays &#8220;I&#8217;m Goin&#8217; Down&#8221; for the first time, wraps up his legendary 1975 stand at the Bottom Line, and more. Plus: a half-hour of 1992 Detroit soundcheck and performance footage!</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 69041, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "