edoll.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 58378, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/15/kingdom-of-days-august-15-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 59369, "position": 2}, "title": "August 15", "author": "Ken", "date": "August 15, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "It's a day for legendary shows, from the 1975 Bottom Line radio broadcast to the '78 Largo video to the stunning, unpredictable second night in Fenway in 2012. Lots of great video and many more highlights inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/bs120815.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/bs120815.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/bs120815.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/bs120815.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/bs120815.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 57120, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/06/20/kingdom-of-days-june-20-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 59369, "position": 3}, "title": "June 20", "author": "Ken", "date": "June 20, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: Bruce plays Red Rocks for the first time, guest stars abound, and the legendary ten-night MSG Reunion stand continues. More highlights inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "h